Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A half-century has passed\Nsince humanity began moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...its burgeoning population into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,These gigantic space cities\Norbiting the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...became a second home to humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...where people were born and raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...and where they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the year 0079 of the Universal Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The space city Side 3 proclaimed itself\Nthe Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It launched a war of independence\Nagainst the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,During this war, the Principality of Zeon\Nand the Federation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...caused the deaths\Nof half the total population.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity was horrified by its own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Re-entry to Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's some soap and a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. You'll be all refreshed\Nwhen you step onto the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro?\N- Come on! You've gotta fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sure it can be fixed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can you fix it?\N- Please let me try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can you really?\N- Thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since he lost his parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...he does nothing but play with this all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They were lost in the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In the One Week Battle.\NHow about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother should still be on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My father went missing at Side 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get to Earth,\NI want to take him to where I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd be able\Nto set foot on Earth again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I came to Side 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...I had a coffee plantation in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever seen these before? Coffee beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When I get back to Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm just going to stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the Zeons were to invade...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the Earth Federation big shots\Norder me to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be buried on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Atmospheric entry in 25 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you can handle it, Mirai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I did an atmospheric entry\Nonce in a space glider.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But that time, I was able to use\Nterrestrial communications networks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was a totally different craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The basic navigation is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow the Salamis's lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just worried because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can't believe that Char has\Nsimply gone away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai, I want you to concentrate entirely\Non the atmospheric entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, kid! Do you read me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lt. Reed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you prepared for atmospheric entry?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll be In the Salamls' re-entry capsule.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll be going faster than your vessel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai, switch to auto-pilot for entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Make all preparations for entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Char's Musai?\N- Still there. But a ship is approaching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is Char trying to\Ntake on supplies again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.\NIf they're getting re-supplied now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...maybe they've given up the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, the three new Zakus\Nreached us in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We enter the atmosphere in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Launching an attack with this kind of timing\Nis unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're pulled in by Earth's gravity,\Nand atmospheric friction begins...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...even a Zaku will burn up in an instant.\NHowever...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the enemy's attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...is completely focused on the entry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...this is our chance to attack with the Zakus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First objective, the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Second objective, the enemy mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We have less than 2 minutes for combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you're capable\Nof carrying out this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those going to Earth will transfer\Nto the re-entry capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the Salamis itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...it will return to Luna II\Nonce the capsule is launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Camilla, are you confident you can\Noutrun the Musai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say that I'm confident.\NBut we can hope for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,According to our data,\Nthe Musai has docked with the Sodon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Either it's being re-supplied,\Nor there's been an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it will come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. I believe that's why I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I must prepare to descend to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Standby with missiles.\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Will Char follow us, I wonder.\N- I doubt it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Salamis capsule is launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base will follow the capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, White Base personnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship will enter the atmosphere\Nin 8 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please be seated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Remain calm, even If there's turbulence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Combat personnel and mechanics{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We may have to deploy the Gundam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mechanics, be on alert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a visual. Maximum magnification.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact estimated in 34 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the hatch!\NLaunch the Gundam immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, return to the White Base\Nafter 4 minutes. No exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Ms. Sayla,\NI don't want to burn up either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Four Zakus to stern, R, 3 degrees.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Four Zakus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But Char shouldn't have any Zakus left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Ms. Sayla?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have to face the facts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can the White Base back me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kai and Ryu will cover you withns.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just watch your altitude.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I watch my altitude\Nin the middle of combat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's launched its mobile suit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me cover, Dren.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll split into two, and then attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Launching re-entry capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready! Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Musai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Missiles behind you!\NLieutenant Reed, please descend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we return?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! We'll just be shot down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Second wave of missiles! Evade!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't the rear defensive\Nmissiles been fired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm, Bright. No one's used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you firing back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was never trained to operate missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something if you don't want to die!\NThere should be a manual somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. The young man who\Nfixed your car will get the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I'll match Char, move for move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times has this been, Amuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you near the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro, don't get too distracted by Char.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Zakus are after the Salamis capsule.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like turning my back on Char, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Char?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The spare bazooka ammo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla, can you send me the beam rifle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible. I can't launch the rifle now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'll ask the mechanics.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take the left machine gun!\N- What?! But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never fired one before either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:11:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu! Hayato!\NThe Zakus are too close for missile fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the machine guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! We can only send you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger! I'll let you know when we launch It.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In front! Amuro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got vulcan guns in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! Lt. Commander Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Commander Char! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Commander Char! Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hit it.\NAre the Vulcan barrels misaligned?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're launching the Gundam Hammer, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The relative speed is too fast...\NCan I catch it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I've lost my spare!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our approach angle's too deep!\NCan we still do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't say for sure, sir! However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceiling...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Reed, your normal suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! We're decompressing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the normal suit sealing tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's on fire! Put it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lieutenant, are you injured?\N- Focus on the suit! The wound will heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir!\N- Can't you be more careful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Salamis capsule's been hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can they still attempt atmospheric entry?\N- I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Bright! At this rate,rom the inside!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, sir.\NThe White Base will bring you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla, tell Amuro to draw away\Nthe two Zakus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!\NHe's got his hands full fighting Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Accelerating by 10%.\NWe'll move in front of the capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Omur! We're bringing in the Salamis capsule.\NGet ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! Ryu! Provide anti-air cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The bastards are moving too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatch is open.\NSalamis capsule, do you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use the laser lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll move automatically once locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope they can pull this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Activating laser lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Crown, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,By now, you should know where\Nthe enemy is firing from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Approach and hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You must use the Zaku's full potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- But sir, the barrage is too intense...!\N- This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Target and hit them from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kom! Can you keep up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lt. Commander! No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only the Zaku's right arm that's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use the heat hawk with my left arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent. You've managed well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hit the enemy's mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! A Zaku's moving in\Nbelow the White Base! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's the situation?\N- Not good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damage on starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire the starboard machine guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploy wall film to the breach! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Block 4, wall film! Anybody there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- I want to go and fight them too!\N- This is a war, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm not afraid!\N- It's really scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the side machine gun turrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Should be in Number 35!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The one on starboard aims forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not letting me get up above him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This pilot's improving rapidly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Kom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, get back to the White Base.\NYou're over the time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger, Ms. Sayla! But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it, Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Crown, get back to Dren's capsule!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Crown. Crown! Can't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Entering atmosphere!\NRaise defense shutters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the Gundam in from the rear hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Securing machine gun turrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, enter from the White Base rear hatch!\NYou're cutting it close!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still have ammo for the vulcans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get him first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Commander Char!\NPlease get in the capsule!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Open the hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, Crown.\NEven that enemy suit wouldn't risk it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Head for the capsule now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Amuro that the Gundam will burn up\Nfrom the atmospheric friction!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here, Amuro! Forget the Zaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My mission here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:17:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...is to safely deliver the White Base\Nand the Gundam to Federation HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the Gundam in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tell Amuro that.\N- This is what happens with amateurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I hadn't sent the Gundam out,\Nthey'd have destroyed the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit down, Lt. Reed.\NIt's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring outer hull cooling system\Nup 3 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you court-martialed! Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro... Hasn't Amuro returned yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The acceleration... I'm falling too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where's Crown?\N- Unfortunately, it's too late to recover him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Commander Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me! I can't slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Commander Char, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Crown... The Zaku isn't capable\Nof atmospheric entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, there's nothing I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But Crown, your death will not be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were able to draw in\Nthe enemy mobile suit with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...we can destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is! Atmospheric entry process!\NBut can I do it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Attitude adjustment... Cooling shift...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Connecting all circuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat-proof film!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The armor temperature's gone down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But how am I going to land?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't monitor the Gundam\Ndue to radio interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Amuro! Please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro... Amuro!\N- We can't make contact for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobile suit hasn't changed position.\NIt's not burning up, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What can this mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it have the ability\Nto enter the atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...given that the Trojan Horse can\Nenter the atmosphere on its own...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...it is possible. Unfortunately for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Altitude 32... 30...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,29... 26... 25... 24...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,20... 17...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,16... 14...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,12... 11...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it going to hold up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When we have radio communications,\Ncontact Captain Garma of the ground forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I understand now,\NLt. Commander Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we weren't able to defeat\Nthe enemy before re-entry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...by making them change\Ntheir approach angle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're forcing the Trojan Horse\Nonto a Zeon-controlled continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A brilliant two-stage operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,War is cruel business.\NI have to plan for every eventuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Captain Garma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what is it, Red Comet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might have to give up that nickname,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're unusually subdued today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever heard of the enemy's Operation V?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've uncovered It.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to Operation V,\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrible. It's that formidable?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've lured the enemy Into your area.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure It'll be good for your record.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll accept your generous gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll intercept them with a Gaw attack carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Emergency launch!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Altitude, 53,000. Decelerating steadily.\NWe're resuming level flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Amuro! Do you read me? Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! The comm should be working now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, please answer me! Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Visuals are back on line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to have a word with him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Federation can beat Zeon\Nwith this mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Radio comm is back. Returning to ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Reception is good.\NAmuro, you can step onto the rear deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now look at that, Pelo! That's Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Is that all land?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And this part over here is called the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I guess this is the first time\Nyou've seen the Earth with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a natural planet, Pelo,\Nmade up of land and sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our projected approach angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our course up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't do us any good, Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. We're deep in Zeon territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is no laughing matter...!\N- Let me take care of that injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Char is a clever strategist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We were led into a trap by Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to break through, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Enemy aircraft approaching!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:22:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's as Char says.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.19,0:22:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to previous Federation ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:22:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...this one's in a class of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.89,0:23:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's the Musai capsule, sir.\N- Good. Bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma Zabi's forces...
